<h1>Adventure Log</h1>

<p>These are a collection of personal logs where I chronical my day to day life, generally on a weekly basis. For my long form, more formal thoughts on a topic, see my <a href="/posts">posts</a>.</p>
<p>You can subscribe via <a href={{metadata.feed.log.xml.path}}>XML-RSS</a> or <a href={{metadata.feed.log.json.path}}>JSON-RSS</a> if you want to stay up to date with my logs.</p>

{% for year in collections.logYears %}
  <h2>{{ year }}</h2>
  {% set collection = collections.logsByYear[year] %}
    <ol class="log-entry_list">
      {% for log in collection  | reverse %}
        <li>
          <a href="{{ log.url }}">{{ log.date | readableDate }}</a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
{% endfor %}
